---
title: Sesame-Crusted Akaroa Salmon with Garlic Spring Onion Rice & Ginger-Soy Veggies
description: Go fishing for compliments with this sublime salmon dish – anyone who tastes the crispy skin speckled with sesame seeds, the
more-ish spring onion and garlic rice or the ginger-soy veggies is going to be falling at your feet in appreciation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sesame-crusted-salmon-garlic-rice-3256d428.jpg
